Package: budgie-droplet-monitor-applet
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Droplet Monitor Applet for the budgie-desktop
 The applet requires a token provided by Digital Ocean.
 The token will be stored in the gnome keyring, so if the keyring is not
 unlocked (i.e. if using auto-login) the applet will not work.
 A token with "Write" scope is needed to start/stop/reboot droplets.
